## ITelemetryData.performanceEntries property

> This API is provided as a beta preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Performance marks and measures collected during the execution of this command. This is an array of `PerformanceEntry` objects, which can include marks, measures, and function timings.

**Signature:**

```typescript
readonly performanceEntries?: readonly PerformanceEntry[];
```
